@.\" $OpenBSD: glxinfo.1,v 1.2 2015/02/03 03:17:20 jsg Exp $
.\" $TOG: xdpyinfo.man /main/22 1998/02/09 13:57:10 kaleb $
.\" Copyright 1988, 1989, 1994, 1998  The Open Group
